reviews.text: Bibo, a hidden gem. Had the degustation, what an amazing meal. The staff were wonderful. Well worth a visit... a little piece of Paris in Hong Kong
Very indulgent degustation menu, every morsel was delectable. Staff were super friendly, decor was intriguing and ambience was on point. Keep the secret well!!
Simply phenomenal food and drinks. The restaurant itself is just one amazing piece of art. A hidden gem on Hong Kong Island
Very good menu, the different flavours are very well mixed . The design makes the experience even better. The wine paring could offer a deeper journey though

The food at Bibo always has the finest details of flavor with the perfect atmosphere. When we dined there, the restaurant was full with a nice buzz and it was great to try their new dishes. I loved the revamped eggplant and celeriac risotto dish!
